metadata.description:
LNRZ ON SOUND WK 10

This song officially marks the end of LNRZ SZN 1, and the beginning of a new chapter. 

A note from the team:

Thank you all for your support in 2022, and for your willingness to grow and collaborate as a unit throughout this curation experiment. LNRZ was founded because a group of friends wanted to release more music together, and it has transformed into something special. Our community has truly given us joy, and we have been working throughout the holidays to properly deliver you an electric SZN 2. 

See you all in the new year. 
2023 is Ours.

Performed by Reo Cragun Produced by DLG. and Clear eyes
(All funds from this drop go to treasury)
